OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1777651869
OL,3,CEvictions, pets, children: What new
OL,4,Crights do renters have from today?
OL,6,FLandlords will no longer be able to
OL,7,Fevict tenants without valid
OL,8,Fjustification and must consider their
OL,9,Frequests to live with a pet, as new
OL,10,Fprotections for private renters come
OL,11,Finto force.
OL,13,FThe Renters' Rights Act, effective
OL,14,Ffrom Friday, signals the end of
OL,15,FSection 21 "no fault" evictions, which
OL,16,Fmeant private landlords could evict
OL,17,Ftenants without providing any reason.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
