CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1777651869
OL,3,CEvictions, pets, children: What new
OL,4,Crights do renters have from today?
OL,6,FRenters will also be protected for a
OL,7,F12-month period at the beginning of a
OL,8,Ftenancy, during which they cannot be
OL,9,Fevicted for a landlord to move in or
OL,10,Fsell the property.
OL,12,FThe new law also prevents landlords
OL,13,Ffrom asking for more than one month's
OL,14,Frent upfront, raising the rent more
OL,15,Fthan once a year, or refusing tenants
OL,16,Fon the basis of them receiving
OL,17,Fbenefits or having children.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
