OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1777651869
OL,3,CEvictions, pets, children: What new
OL,4,Crights do renters have from today?
OL,6,FIt expands protections for tenants who
OL,7,Ftemporarily fall into rent arrears, by
OL,8,Fincreasing the mandatory threshold for
OL,9,Feviction from two months' arrears to
OL,10,Fthree.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FTenancies in the private rented sector
OL,18,Fwill also roll on from month to month
OL,19,For week to week, giving renters more
OL,20,Fflexibility, rather than having fixed
OL,21,Fcontracts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
