OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1777651869
OL,3,CEvictions, pets, children: What new
OL,4,Crights do renters have from today?
OL,6,FRenters can end them with two months'
OL,7,Fnotice, the law says.
OL,9,FThe new rules have penalties of up to
OL,10,F#7,000 for initial breaches, rising to
OL,11,F#40,000 or even criminal prosecution
OL,12,Ffor repeated violations.
OL,14,FA new Private Rented Sector Landlord
OL,15,FOmbudsman Service is being introduced,
OL,16,Fthat will allow renters to seek
OL,17,Fguidance or complain about their
OL,18,Fliving situation for free.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
