CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1777651869
OL,3,CEvictions, pets, children: What new
OL,4,Crights do renters have from today?
OL,6,FThe service will have the powers to
OL,7,Fcompel landlords to issue an apology,
OL,8,Fprovide information, take remedial
OL,9,Faction, or even pay compensation if
OL,10,Fnecessary.
OL,12,FTenants will also be able to seek rent
OL,13,Frepayment orders against their
OL,14,Flandlord if they persistently fail to
OL,15,Fjoin the service.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
