OL,3,CEvictions, pets, children: What new
OL,4,Crights do renters have from today?
OL,6,F"For too long, families have lived
OL,7,Fwith the constant fear of eviction,
OL,8,Fwhile young people have been outbid
OL,9,Ffor the homes they need to start their
OL,10,Flives," Prime Minister Keir Starmer
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,F"Today we are putting that right. We
OL,14,Fpromised to fix a broken rental system
OL,15,Fand we're delivering.
OL,17,F"This historic action will make
OL,18,Frenting fairer, safer and more secure
OL,19,Ffor millions, so people can settle,
OL,20,Fput down roots and build their lives."
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
