OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1777651869
OL,3,CEvictions, pets, children: What new
OL,4,Crights do renters have from today?
OL,6,FHousing charity Shelter estimated that
OL,7,Fmore than 2,000 households a month
OL,8,Fwill be protected "from the threat of
OL,9,Fhomelessness" directly caused by no-
OL,10,Ffault evictions under the law.
OL,12,FAt the end of December 2025, there
OL,13,Fwere 4,960 households in England that
OL,14,Fneeded help to prevent them becoming
OL,15,Fhomeless after they were served a
OL,16,Fsection 21 notice, government data
OL,17,Fpublished on Thursday showed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
