OL,3,CEvictions, pets, children: What new
OL,4,Crights do renters have from today?
OL,6,FJoanna Elson, chief executive at
OL,7,FIndependent Age, a charity supporting
OL,8,Fpensioners in the UK, said: "Many of
OL,9,Fthe tenants in later life that we
OL,10,Fspeak to say that, until now, they
OL,11,Flived in a constant state of anxiety,
OL,12,Fworried about being evicted for no
OL,13,Freason and the consequences of asking
OL,14,Ftheir landlord for repairs.
OL,16,F"Although the job of making renting
OL,17,Fsafe, secure and affordable for
OL,18,Feveryone is not yet done, today we are
OL,19,Fa significant step closer."
OL,26,@pD@]OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
