OL,3,CEvictions, pets, children: What new
OL,4,Crights do renters have from today?
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FPrivate landlords who have issued
OL,12,Ftheir tenants a Section 21 before May
OL,13,F1 are still able to go through with
OL,14,Fthe process, but the notices will
OL,15,Fexpire on July 31 or within six
OL,16,Fmonths; whichever comes first.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
