CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1777651869
OL,3,CEvictions, pets, children: What new
OL,4,Crights do renters have from today?
OL,6,FLandlords who have issued a Section 8
OL,7,F- which requires a legally defined
OL,8,Freason for eviction - also have until
OL,9,FJuly 31 or 12 months since the notice
OL,10,Fdate; whichever comes first.
OL,12,F"Tenants are often among the lowest
OL,13,Fearners and need the extra help,"
OL,14,FAndrea Egan, Unison general secretary,
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,F"But the next step must be to
OL,18,Fintroduce rent controls. That will
OL,19,Fstop landlords forcing people out by
OL,20,Fratcheting up fees to unaffordable
OL,21,Flevels."
OL,26,@tD@AOUyD@AOU}D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
