OL,3,CEvictions, pets, children: What new
OL,4,Crights do renters have from today?
OL,6,FThe act does include strengthened
OL,7,Frights for landlords to reclaim
OL,8,Fproperties when necessary, for
OL,9,Fexample, to sell or move in, the
OL,10,FMinistry of Housing, Communities and
OL,11,FLocal Government says.
OL,13,FWhen using these grounds, landlords
OL,14,Fwill need to provide four months'
OL,15,Fnotice, giving tenants more time to
OL,16,Ffind a new home.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
