CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1777651869
OL,3,CEvictions, pets, children: What new
OL,4,Crights do renters have from today?
OL,6,FTo prevent landlords from abusing the
OL,7,Fmoving in and selling grounds,
OL,8,Flandlords will not be able to market
OL,9,For re-let their property for 12 months
OL,10,Fafter using the moving or selling
OL,11,Fgrounds.
OL,13,FThere is an exception to this
OL,14,Frestriction for shared owners when
OL,15,Fthey use the selling ground (Ground
OL,16,F1A) where they can demonstrate they
OL,17,Fhave made a genuine attempt to sell
OL,18,Ftheir property.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
